title: Perspective
content:
If you change the way _you_ look at things, the things you look at change.

- Wayne Dyer

title: Best Life
content: Live your best, and act your best, and think your best each day, for there may be no tomorrows.

title: Hey, you
content:
The argument of whether it get better or worse is down to **you**. _It_ is not a thing, that's just what you call your current situation. \
And who better to trust with your own life than yourself.
